{"tid":400444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇蟲蟲專家幫手睇下咩黎","createTime":"2017-09-14T20:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T02:29:23.000Z","uid":28912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1eb5e26448cdc7a1c8663f4d84d5f28c600aa7","tid":400444,"uid":28912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/035339_84c4a1fd3d39a16c75c8e1f3ed8434a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F035339_84c4a1fd3d39a16c75c8e1f3ed8434a5.jpg&h=f42f5558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前日執屋見到個收納盒有兩三隻細細粒 淺啡色的蟲仔驚到掉左出去 。其實之前偶然大脾成日比野咬到一串串咬痕<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/035617_278c4830115e591383c75b09c1b5615b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F035617_278c4830115e591383c75b09c1b5615b.jpg&h=62a7b836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似 禁啦<br />\n就諗住係公司比野咬 本身唔覺得屋企有事，<br />\n但唔知琴日定今日又比野咬...<br />\n究竟圖入面係未真係有蚤，定我心理作用 個d係一其他昆蟲（好似8隻腳）<br />\n床褥底又唔見有蟲<br />\n上網睇完資料周圍搵又唔覺有其他蹟像有<br />\n<br />\nbtw 屋企幾多紙箱放野 但前兩日執野唔覺有蟲喎...<br />\n<br />\n利申 好驚蟲 ,心理作用定點周身痕，冇覺好訓 救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7938cb2749841176b9d608d4fdab9613b27e26","tid":400444,"uid":3698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:19:24.000Z","msg":"哦～～～～你仆街啦<br />\n以為貼個無毛西扮手臂會呃到人"},{"pid":"94ba8226f8827807b28b208cd2157a41a9c0d1ed","tid":400444,"uid":41759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"好性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e445892